<style>
    /* Parallax & Animations */
    .parallax-bg {
        background-attachment: fixed;
        background-position: center;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-size: cover;
    }

    @keyframes fade-in-up {
        from {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(40px);
        }

        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    }

    .animate-entry {
        opacity: 0;
        animation: fade-in-up 1s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) forwards;
    }

    .reveal {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(30px);
        transition: all 1s ease-out;
    }

    .reveal.active {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
    }

    /* Custom Timeline Line */
    .timeline-line::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 50%;
        width: 2px;
        height: 100%;
        background: #e2e8f0;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        z-index: 0;
    }
</style>

<div id="preloader"
    class="fixed inset-0 z-[9999] bg-slate-900 flex flex-col items-center justify-center transition-opacity duration-700 ease-out">
    <div class="relative w-24 h-24 mb-6">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 border-t-4 border-cyan-500 rounded-full animate-spin"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-3 border-b-4 border-white/20 rounded-full animate-spin"
            style="animation-direction: reverse; animation-duration: 2s;"></div>
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-white text-xl font-bold tracking-widest uppercase animate-pulse">Our Story</h2>
</div>

<div class="relative h-[85vh] parallax-bg flex items-center justify-center text-center px-4"
    style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552674605-db6ffd4facb5?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1950&q=80');">

    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate-900/50 backdrop-blur-[2px]"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="animate-entry" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
            <span
                class="inline-block py-1 px-4 rounded-full bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 text-cyan-100 text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-6 shadow-xl">
                The Origin
            </span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="animate-entry text-6xl md:text-8xl text-white font-black mb-8 drop-shadow-2xl leading-tight"
            style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
            It started with a<br><span
                class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-400">Single Breath.</span>
        </h1>
    </div>

    <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce text-white/50">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path>
        </svg>
    </div>
</div>

<section class="py-24 bg-white relative">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="relative -mt-40 mb-12 text-center reveal">
            <div class="inline-block relative">
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-400 to-blue-600 rounded-full blur opacity-50 transform translate-y-4">
                </div>
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552374196-c4e7ffc6e126?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=400"
                    class="relative w-40 h-40 md:w-56 md:h-56 rounded-full object-cover border-8 border-white shadow-2xl">
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">Alex Mercer</h2>
                <p class="text-cyan-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm">Founder & Head Coach</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate mx-auto leading-relaxed text-slate-600 reveal">
            <p
                class="first-letter:text-7xl first-letter:font-black first-letter:text-slate-900 first-letter:mr-3 first-letter:float-left">
                <%= locals.site ? site.founderStory
                    : 'Chill Thrive was born not from ambition, but from necessity. Five years ago, I was burned out, disconnected, and running on adrenaline. My nervous system was fried. I tried meditation, I tried medication, but nothing could quiet the noise.'
                    %>
            </p>
            <p>
                Then I found the cold. That first plunge was terrifying. Every instinct screamed at me to get out. But
                in that chaos, I found a silence I hadn't heard in years.
            </p>
            <p>
                I realized that recovery isn't passive. You don't "wait" to feel better. You have to actively train your
                body to find calm in the storm. That is what we build here. Not just ice baths, but resilience for life.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

